1.00	Rebellion_(Escape_Velocity)	Escape Velocity (video game)	Escape Velocity is a single-player role-playing space trading and combat video game series first introduced in 1996 by Ambrosia Software for the Apple Macintosh. Two other similar games based on the original, EV Override and EV Nova, followed in 1998 and 2002 respectively, the latter of which is also available on Microsoft Windows. In addition there is a trading card game available based on the storyline of the EV Nova universe.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/6/6a/Escape-Velocity-title.png/250px-Escape-Velocity-title.png
